ost_step.2: Subtract the amount of money he spent from the initial amount. He spent 4 dollars. So, he had 33 - 4 = 29 dollars left.
ost_step.3: Add the amount of money Oliver received from his mom to the remaining amount. He got 32 dollars from his mom. So, Oliver now has 29 dollars + 32 dollars = 61 dollars.
